Package: langtropy
Title: Information-Theoretic Measures for Linguistic Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Vladimir", "Buskin", , "VBuskin@ku.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "orcid.org/0009-0005-5824-1012"))
Description: Provides functions to calculate information-theoretic measures 
    commonly used in linguistic analysis, including surprisal, entropy, 
    mutual information, and other measures of information content in 
    linguistic data.
